cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

The paper deals with visual tracking using deep learning and probabilistic filtering techniques, which are commonly studied in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also involves motion analysis and tracking, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
